  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <p style="font-size:1.15rem;color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:700;margin:30px 0 18px">From $1,141 per person</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Highlights</h2>
    <ul style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Stand on the slopes of the world&#39;s only active carbonatite volcano.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Conquer a challenging, steep volcanic ash climb for an ultimate adrenaline rush.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:8px">Gaze out at breathtaking, lunar-like panoramas over the glowing pink waters of Lake Natron.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">A Day on This Trip</h2>
    <ol style="padding-left:22px;margin-bottom:8px">
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">Midnight (12:00 AM): Due to intense daytime heat on the barren slopes, the steep climb begins in the cool of the night.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">05:30 AM: Arrive at the summit area in time to witness an unforgettable, dramatic sunrise over the Great Rift Valley.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">07:00 AM: Carefully navigate the steep, loose volcanic ash and gravel paths back down the mountain.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">11:00 AM: Reach the base of the mountain for a well-deserved breakfast/brunch at camp before exploring the shores of Lake Natron.</li>
<li style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:10px">02:00 PM: Drive back across the rugged desert tracks to Arusha.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Private 4x4 transport to remote Lake Natron, specialized mountain/Maasai guide fees, village/local authority conservation fees, meals, and emergency first aid support.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">What is Not Included</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Technical hiking poles (highly recommended), specialized trekking gear, tips for mountain crew, and personal insurance.</p>
    <p style="font-size:.92rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-top:18px">Every day trip is private and fully customisable. Prices vary with group size and season, so message Nelson for an exact quote for your dates.</p>
